<http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#Geometry> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#Geometry> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The locn:Geometry class provides the means to identify a location as a point, line, polygon, etc. expressed using coordinates in some coordinate reference system." .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#Geometry> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/usageNote> "This specification does not impose any additional requirements to properties for this entity." .
